Gamepad 1 controls: (Driver)
Left stick: Forward/backward, strafe left/right
Right stick: Turn left/right
Dpad: Turn left/right
Right bumper: Slow mode

Gamepad 2 controls:  (Operator)
Left stick: arm up/down (lower half)
Left bumper: Close intake
Right bumper: Open intake
B: Arm speed up (for low battery situations)
Y: Arm Super slow
X: Arm Slow